name: CDCalculator
0:
”Alexa, open CD calculator”
”Alexa, launch CD calculator”
”Alexa, start CD calculator”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: c. d. calculator
des: Calculates the ending balance of a CD when the interest is compounded daily and annually. You will have to provide the initial deposit amount, interest rate, and term in months. You can start over and try a different combination of CD by saying start over.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
